{"componentChunkName":"component---src-components-blog-post-js","path":"/sliding-window/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"what-is-a-sliding-window\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#what-is-a-sliding-window\" aria-label=\"what is a sliding window permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>What is a <code class=\"language-jstext\">sliding window</code></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>길거나 짧은 sequence를 특정할 때\n<ul>\n<li>주로 <code class=\"language-jstext\">array</code>, <code class=\"language-jstext\">string</code>에 사용</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>time complextity <code class=\"language-jstext\">O(k*n)</code>\n<ul>\n<li>Brute force의 경우 <code class=\"language-jstext\">O(n^2)</code></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"접근방식\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A0%91%EA%B7%BC%EB%B0%A9%EC%8B%9D\" aria-label=\"접근방식 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>접근방식</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>fast / slow\n<ul>\n<li>fast slow 모두 나란히 증가</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/maximum-number-of-vowels-in-a-substring-of-given-length\">Maximum Number of Vowels in a Substring of Given Length</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>fast / catchup\n<ul>\n<li>후순위 탐색이 faster point까지 한 번에 따라잡음</li>\n<li>Maximum consecutive sum</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/maximum-average-subarray-i\">Maximum Average Subarray I</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>fast / 따라가기\n<ul>\n<li>선행 탐색 이후 slower 결정</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/house-robber\">lagging</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>front / back\n<ul>\n<li>시작과 끝에서 각자 탐색</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h1 id=\"출처\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%B6%9C%EC%B2%98\" aria-label=\"출처 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>출처</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/a/64111403\">What is Sliding Window Algorithm? Examples?</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://medium.com/outco/how-to-solve-sliding-window-problems-28d67601a66\">How to Solve Sliding Window Problems</a></p>\n</blockquote>","frontmatter":{"title":"Sliding window","date":"January 27, 2024","spoiler":"Dynamic Programming"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/sliding-window/"}},"staticQueryHashes":["63159454"],"slicesMap":{}}